<span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">autoreap</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>
<span class=\"p\">}</span>
</code></pre></div>
<p>可以看到如果父进程对子进程的生死不关心，那么设置autoreap为TRUE，甚至这个信号也可以不发送了。</p>" "http://cyukang.com/2013/11/23/kernel-analysis-process-defunct.html" (21136 24704) old 2 nil nil ((title nil "Kernel analysis: Defunct Process") (link ((href . "http://cyukang.com/2013/11/23/kernel-analysis-process-defunct.html"))) (updated nil "2013-11-23T00:00:00-08:00") (id nil "http://cyukang.com/2013/11/23/kernel-analysis-process-defunct") (content ((type . "html")) "
<p>我发现带着问题去看内核代码比较容易理解。如果一个父进程显示的设置SIGCHLD为Ignore，子进程将自己清理自己。</p>

<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"cpp\"><span class=\"cp\">#include &lt;signal.h&gt;</span>
<span class=\"cp\">#include &lt;unistd.h&gt;</span>
