<a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"/images/static3.jpg\"><img class=\"img-center size-full wp-image-111\" title=\"static3\" src=\"/images/static3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"317\" height=\"148\" /></a>

